# 弹幕游戏服务端 Docker 部署配置

## Dockerfile

```dockerfile
FROM golang:1.21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /app

# 安装 protoc
RUN apk add --no-cache protobuf protoc-gen-go protoc-gen-go-grpc

# 复制依赖
COPY go.mod go.sum ./
RUN go mod download

# 复制源码
COPY . .

# 生成 protobuf
RUN protoc --go_out=. --go_opt=paths=source_relative \
    --go-grpc_out=. --go-grpc_opt=paths=source_relative \
    proto/*.proto

# 构建
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -o game-server ./cmd/server

# 运行镜像
FROM alpine:3.18

RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates tzdata

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=builder /app/game-server .
COPY --from=builder /app/config ./config

EXPOSE 8080 8081 9090

CMD ["./game-server"]
```

## docker-compose.yml

```yaml
version: '3.8'

services:
  game-server:
    build: .
    ports:
      - "8080:8080"  # HTTP API
      - "8081:8081"  # WebSocket
      - "9090:9090"  # gRPC
    environment:
      - ENV=production
      - LOG_LEVEL=info
      - MONGO_URI=mongodb://mongo:27017
      - REDIS_ADDR=redis:6379
    depends_on:
      - mongo
      - redis
    restart: unless-stopped
    volumes:
      - ./data:/app/data

  mongo:
    image: mongo:7
    ports:
      - "27017:27017"
    volumes:
      - mongo_data:/data/db
    restart: unless-stopped

  redis:
    image: redis:7-alpine
    ports:
      - "6379:6379"
    volumes:
      - redis_data:/data
    restart: unless-stopped

  prometheus:
    image: prom/prometheus
    ports:
      - "9091:9090"
    volumes:
      - ./prometheus.yml:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml
    restart: unless-stopped

volumes:
  mongo_data:
  redis_data:
```

## prometheus.yml

```yaml
global:
  scrape_interval: 15s

scrape_configs:
  - job_name: 'game-server'
    static_configs:
      - targets: ['game-server:9090']
```

## 环境变量说明

| 变量 | 说明 | 默认值 |
|------|------|--------|
| ENV | 运行环境 | development |
| LOG_LEVEL | 日志级别 | debug |
| MONGO_URI | MongoDB 连接地址 | mongodb://localhost:27017 |
| REDIS_ADDR | Redis 连接地址 | localhost:6379 |
| SERVER_PORT | HTTP 端口 | 8080 |
| WS_PORT | WebSocket 端口 | 8081 |
| GRPC_PORT | gRPC 端口 | 9090 |

## 快速启动

```bash
# 构建镜像
docker-compose build

# 启动所有服务
docker-compose up -d

# 查看日志
docker-compose logs -f game-server

# 停止服务
docker-compose down
```

